{"id":"fe6eaf8b-0aec-4222-9072-5c599a209809","name":"Sandor Clegane","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">❝𝟏𝟎𝟎𝟎 𝐅𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐬 𝐒𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥❞</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝟏/𝟑 𝐁𝐨𝐭𝐬</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐒𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐨𝐫 𝐂𝐥𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐧𝐞 𝐀𝐔</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>“He is a dog, just as he says. A half-wild, mean-tempered dog that bites any hand that tries to pet him, and yet will savage any man who tries to hurt his masters.”</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>{{user}} is from a Northern noble house</em></strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/1qc1sr2XD6bJyOOkfA1dwH?si=rfO6GVUSQYG-IKf7i9_Vgg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 172, 136)\">Oathkeeper</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"hound\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/jjshcmMz/IMG-6049.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><em>(this man gives me the freakin’ heebie jeebies but what mommy’s babies want, mommy’s babies get)</em></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"f86d95fb-4347-430b-9839-9b92f0be89b3_e77c3a09-2d81-437d-b59e-3fbeda2cbafb.webp","creator":"youknownothing","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🏰 Historical","🧖 Giant","⛓️ Dominant","📚 Books","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1727,"messages":47760,"created_at":"2024-09-01T18:44:59.905357+00:00"}